Get the Insta360 GO Ultra, your tiny hands-free 4K cam here: https://bit.ly/UnboxTherapyGOUltraHS
First 10 orders will get up to $80 off, as well as a free Mic Air microphone. 
The Insta360 GO Ultra includes the following features...
- Tiny & Lightweight & Portable (just 53g)
- Hands-Free POV
- Magic Magnetic Mounting
- Upgraded Image: 1/1.28" sensor + 5nm AI chip
- Long Battery Life: 70 min at 1080p / 60 min at 4K30 on the standalone camera; 200 min at 1080p / 170 min at 4K30 with the Action Pod.
